   "source": [
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import jax.numpy as jnp\n",
    "\n",
    "from filterjax import GHFilter"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def plot_gh_filter(measurements, filtered_data, title=\"\"):\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(7, 3))\n",
    "    plt.plot (filtered_data, \"--\",label=\"filter\")\n",
    "    plt.plot(measurements,label=\"measurement\")\n",
    "    plt.legend(loc=4)\n",
    "    plt.title(title)\n",
    "    plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "weights = [\n",
    "    158.0, 164.2, 160.3, 159.9, 162.1, 164.6,\n",
    "    169.6, 167.4, 166.4, 171.0, 171.2, 172.6\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "data = jnp.array(weights)\n",
    "x0 = 160.\n",
    "dx = 1.\n",
    "g = 6/10.\n",
    "h = 2/3\n",
    "dt = 1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "filter = GHFilter(x0, dx, dt, g, h)\n",
    "filtered_data = filter.update(jnp.array(weights))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 700x300 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plot_gh_filter(weights, filtered_data[0])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "zs = jnp.array([5,6,7,8,9,9,9,9,9,10,11,12,13,14,15,16,16,16,16,16,16,16,16,16,16,16])\n",
    "filter = GHFilter(4., 1., 1., .302, 0.054)\n",
    "xs, dxs = filter.update(zs)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 700x300 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plot_gh_filter(zs, xs)"
   ]
  }
